  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to assess the effect of ranibizumab in reducing intraoperative
      vitreous haemorrhage during pars plana vitrectomy, thus facilitating surgery and improving
      its anatomical and functional results in patients with advanced proliferative diabetic
      retinopathy and traction retinal detachment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
